sentences.english: Shows page setup for printing the active table or query.
sentences.chinese: 显示当前表格或查询的列印页面设置。

sentences.english: Hey guys n gals try this if u have guts to score high n high.

sentences.english: You may use an online printer to print out the data.

sentences.english: Please fill it out online, print it out, and bring it with you when you enroll to NCKU.

sentences.english: All that remained was printing and hand-binding the books…

sentences.english: If your hand-writing is not clear, type the answers.

sentences.english: Essay manuscripts should be typewritten, double-spaced, etc.

sentences.english: Machine offers a surface for the substrate to be printed and the screen is secured by the upper section.

sentences.english: Promote the use of multiple screen method in printing on-line enquiries.
sentences.chinese: 鼓励员工在联机查询时，使用多重画面功能列印。
